          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Fragments of a life of Severus, patriarch of Antioch , written by the author, whose name is not mentioned in the portions extant, at the request of one Domitius. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 1 item.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
